Name: Wrestling Manager 2023
About the game: Wrestling Manager 2023 is an easy-to-use game where you manage a wrestling company, and bring it to the top! Main Features: *Book shows Make the crowd be on their feet! *Manage workers Keep them happy and safe! *Build PPV Cards Create matches for a PPV, and build status around them! *Create stables Make groups of workers wrestle together! *Hire new workers Get workers from rivalry companies or the wrestling development! *Create new Championships Introduce new gold to your company! *Customize your workers With many customizables you can make your workers outfit in many different ways! *Promises Make and keep promises made with your workers! *Get earnings from merchandises Earn money by selling your wrestler's merchandise! *Create Roster Pack Make your own roster pack, including workers, companies, championships, shows and so on...
